## Kako funkcionira

### 1. Slanje poruke i logiranje

**Request:**
```bash
POST /api/chat/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 123,
    "message": "Kako napraviti tortu?",
    "messageType": "Recipe"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "response": "Odgovor agenta...",
    "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:45.123Z"
}
```

### 2. Tokovi logiranja

```
User Message
    ↓
ChatController.SendMessage()
    ↓
ChatLogger.LogChatMessage()
    ├─→ LogToJson() - Sprema u chat-log-YYYY-MM-DD.json
    ├─→ LogToCsv()  - Sprema u chat-log-YYYY-MM-DD.csv
    └─→ InvokePowerShellLogger() - Pokreće PowerShell skriptu
        ├─→ Sprema detaljnu poruku u chat-log-YYYY-MM-DD.log
        ├─→ Sprema JSON backup u YYYY-MM-DD-messages.jsonl
        ├─→ Arhivira datoteke starije od 30 dana
        └─→ Kompresira datoteke starije od 90 dana
```

