## Format logiranih podataka

### JSON Format
```json
[
  {
    "timestamp": "2024-01-15 10:30:45.123",
    "userId": 123,
    "userMessage": "Kako napraviti tortu?",
    "agentResponse": "Trebatćeš brašno, jaja, šećer...",
    "messageType": "Recipe",
    "sessionId": "a1b2c3d4"
  }
]
```

### CSV Format
```
Timestamp,UserId,UserMessage,AgentResponse,MessageType
"2024-01-15 10:30:45.123",123,"Kako napraviti tortu?","Trebatćeš brašno, jaja, šećer...","Recipe"
```

### PowerShell Log Format
```
[2024-01-15 10:30:45.123] ========================================
Timestamp: 2024-01-15 10:30:45.123
User ID: 123
Message Type: Recipe
Session ID: a1b2c3d4
----------------------------------------
USER MESSAGE:
Kako napraviti tortu?
----------------------------------------
AGENT RESPONSE:
Trebatćeš brašno, jaja, šećer...
========================================
```

